¡Cielos, Hajime!

1401
01:29:25,170 --> 01:29:26,210
Why y-

1402
01:29:28,340 --> 01:29:29,440
¿Por qué--?

1403
01:29:29,440 --> 01:29:31,220
¿Ya te refrescaste?

1404
01:29:32,220 --> 01:29:34,180
¡Maldita Miyuki!

1405
01:29:54,780 --> 01:29:56,700

1406
01:29:58,680 --> 01:30:00,610

1407
